metadata.name: Kate MacDonald Airdrops
metadata.description: Kate MacDonald is a multidisciplinary artist based in Vancouver, BC who joined the NFT community in February 2021. Her paintings, digital collages and video art have been exhibited throughout North America and Europe, and her paintings have been featured in Wired and international editions of GQ magazine. She has been twice recognized as a Top Ten Digital Artist by the Los Angeles Center for Digital Art (LACDA) - in 2012 and 2017.
